methods.name: highlight
methods.docstring:
Apply highlighting in place to text.

Args:
    text (~Text): A text object highlight.

classes.name: NullHighlighter
classes.docstring:
A highlighter object that doesn't highlight.

May be used to disable highlighting entirely.

classes.name: RegexHighlighter
classes.docstring: Applies highlighting from a list of regular expressions.

methods.name: highlight
methods.docstring:
Highlight :class:`rich.text.Text` using regular expressions.

Args:
    text (~Text): Text to highlighted.

classes.name: ReprHighlighter
classes.docstring: Highlights the text typically produced from ``__repr__`` methods.

classes.name: ISO8601Highlighter
classes.docstring:
Highlights the ISO8601 date time strings.
